rem Outside Hotel
rem 8/18/2017

do Examine Hotel
 [
  print It's a run down building that houses too many people. They offer rooms no 
  print bigger than coffins and you have to pay by the day. The showers and restrooms 
  print are public, and the electricity is intermintent at best.
 ]

do Enter Hotel
 [
  ifflag oldman gone
   [
    print You walk up the short stoop, finding an empty couch and an overworked
    print attendant behind the counter.
    go Cheap Hotel
   |
    print You walk up the short stoop, finding an old man sitting on a couch and an
    print overworked attendant behind the counter.
    go Cheap Hotel
   ]
 ]

do Walk North
 [
  print You walk north watching your back, stopping at the cafe.
  go Outside Cafe
 ]